data.description: Welcome to Forest Hills Park. You will find this home tucked away at the end of a cul-de-sac on over an acre of private land. Upstairs find a large living area and kitchen, Three bedrooms and a full bath. Downstairs there is another bedroom, garage access, a utility room,  a stunning bathroom and a huge flex space that could be used for so many different options. Outside find plenty of parking, a large deck, a spacious yard and some beautiful trees to wander through. All this in quiet area that is only minutes from town.
